玩的事情，他们永远都是，和你有关系吗；我和他们说我的琐事，永远回答，你的事情怎么那么多。高三了，我明白必须要努力起来了，但是他们的这种教育方式，我真的不想再努力了。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I4oGI7den/ZllEAMaCDgzMTIyMzA0IOjuzpYGMAM4pAFAJHIJNTQzNzc4Nzc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"26 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e6486885659f20ab7109eab3d6aa48c4_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"37_1658160990.5889814","card_id":"Q_538242334","target":{"id":538242334,"title":"当钢琴老师最低需要达到什么演奏水平?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/538242334","type":"question","created":1655482684,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":46,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[549,167612,595391],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"本人不是从小科班出身，小学学过两年半的电子琴考了十级，长大大学毕业后又自考了音乐学院的专升本。学习了乐理和声等基础课程。线下也有请教培训班老师，她说我现在可以去当陪练了，可我只有弹到849初段（可能因为我每次作业完成很好不过还是挺心虚)，一个是在我们三线城市陪练需求很低二是我想再在家里多练练到时候直接找老师工作这样比较节省时间成本吧？先抛开教学水平，在这里我只想问一问最低标准的钢琴老师需要达到什么演奏和视奏硬性标准呢？大家有什么建议吗？谢谢大家帮忙。"},"attached_info":"Cj4I4oGI7den/ZllEAMaCDgxODkxNDAyILzSspUGMAI4LkAlcgk1MzgyNDIzMzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"26 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-fdabdaeb73432639d03fff461191ffa0_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"38_1658160990.5898244","card_id":"Q_537811154","target":{"id":537811154,"title":"如何理解官方翻译很多情况下翻译的词与原本英语发音相差较大？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/537811154","type":"question","created":1655267511,"answer_count":24,"follower_count":61,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[165,5430],"comment_count":15,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"(发音是一隆马斯克 改成埃隆、扣比改成科比，川普改成特朗普)"},"attached_info":"Cj4I4oGI7den/ZllEAMaCDgxNzk1